// Wall-clock backstop per agent — catches a GENUINELY hung agent overnight without
// ever cutting off a productive build. We do NOT cap turn-count: a high turn-count
// round can be productive (a real run built an entire page in 228 turns / ~15 min).
// Budgets are deliberately generous (≈2× the longest real run) so only true hangs trip.
const WORKER_WALL_MS = Number(process.env.WORKER_WALL_MS ?? 30 * 60_000); // workers: 30 min
const REASON_WALL_MS = Number(process.env.REASON_WALL_MS ?? 5 * 60_000);  // tool-less reasoning: 5 min

